	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yes, it is a PAL one, I ran it on PAL TV set that does not support NTSC at all, and it felt xactly like Dendy speed-wise. I think almost all the built-in games are NTSC versions. I haven't made any direct comparison tests yet, though, would be interesting to see if it has switched the duty cycle bug, for example.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


